* Fetch only the last 1M of the log file
* Copy files in 1M chunks (rather than attempting to read whole files into memory)
* Avoid racing with the camera (background service)
* Avoid restarting the background service if it's already running
* Avoid racing between the worker and the background service

1.0 (6)

* Don't try to copy directories!
* Beef up checks when moving files.
* Write out a log that the app can read (and display it in the app).
* Launching/resuming the activity restarts work/service if they have stopped.

1.0 (5)

* Allow running a persistent, foreground service to monitor for files in real-time.
